title: Valle Poniente Vegetarian
description: Vegetarian restaurant offering a concise menu of homestyle food. A plate of tacos with your choice of corn or whole wheat tortillas and comes with fresh vegetables. Has fresh juices, vegetarian pozole, and more. Also a well-stocked grocery shop selling imported & domestic health foods.
